{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "a90b4d45-7f99-4621-a5c2-12759e6659c9",
		"name": "Pizzaria ECA - Test Suite",
		"description": "Suite de testes da Pizzaria ECA (TF2 - microsservicos). TODO o acesso passa pelo API Gateway (http://localhost:8080).\n\nAutenticacao: o gateway usa JWT Bearer. O login (UC2) captura o token automaticamente na variavel `jwt_token`. Requests que exigem outro usuario (ADMIN, etc.) fazem auto-login via pre-request script.\n\nRotas:\n- /auth/** -> gateway (login/registro, publico)\n- /api/** -> pizzaria-service (StripPrefix=1)\n- /api-estoque/** -> estoque-service\n\nUsuarios do seed (senha 123456): huguinho.pato@email.com (CLIENTE, fidelidade), zezinho.pato@email.com (CLIENTE, dono do pedido 8), patinhas@email.com (ADMIN), margarida@email.com (ADMIN).",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
	"item": [
		{
			"name": "01. Autenticacao e Registro",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "UC1 - Registrar Novo Cliente",
					"request": {
						"auth": {
							"type": "noauth"
						},
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json",
								"type": "text"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"cpf\": \"9007\",\n  \"nome\": \"Peninha Pato\",\n  \"celular\": \"51999999999\",\n  \"endereco\": \"Rua da Patolandia, 500\",\n  \"email\": \"peninha@email.com\",\n  \"senha\": \"123456\"\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/registrar",
							"host": [
								"{{baseUrl}}"
							],
							"path": [
								"auth",
								"registrar"
							]
						},
						"description": "Registra um novo cliente (UC11). Rota publica no gateway: /auth/registrar (sem /api)."
					},
					"response": []
				},
				{
					"name": "UC2 - Autenticar Cliente (Login)",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"const res = pm.response.json();",
									"if (res && res.token) {",
									"    pm.collectionVariables.set(\"jwt_token\", res.token);",
									"    console.log(\"JWT (huguinho) salvo em jwt_token.\");",
									"} else {",
									"    console.warn(\"Login nao retornou token:\", JSON.stringify(res));",
									"}"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"auth": {
							"type": "noauth"
						},
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json",
								"type": "text"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"huguinho.pato@email.com\",\n  \"senha\": \"123456\"\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/login",
							"host": [
								"{{baseUrl}}"
							],
							"path": [
								"auth",
								"login"
							]
						},
						"description": "Autentica Huguinho Pato (UC12). Rota publica: /auth/login. O script de teste salva o JWT retornado (campo `token`) na variavel `jwt_token`, usada por padrao em todas as requisicoes protegidas."
					},
					"response": []
				}
			]
		},
